Author: SHossain#0007
Content: adaptivepow helps chains that are 100% minable. imagine if KMDICE chain is being mined by only CPU, diff is low for that and suddenly a big miner comes in with a lot of hash to mine some blocks quickly and goes for mining another chain. KMDICE would be left with very high diff and normal CPU miners will have to try for a year with CPU to get the next block. adaptivepow helps in this scenerio to mine a block with CPU within 10-15 after the big ASIC miner left the chain.
